     1‚Üí/**
     2‚Üí * MMS Man-hour Leveling Worker Processor
     3‚Üí *
     4‚Üí * BullMQ job processor for workload balancing across time periods.
     5‚Üí * Projects workforce requirements and generates adjustment recommendations
     6‚Üí * to prevent overload/underutilization of depot maintenance resources.
     7‚Üí *
     8‚Üí * Leveling Strategies (priority order):
     9‚Üí * 1. ADVANCE_PM (1.1x cost, LOW risk)
    10‚Üí * 2. DEFER_PM (1.05x cost, LOW risk)
    11‚Üí * 3. ADD_OVERTIME (1.5x cost, NO risk)
    12‚Üí * 4. CROSS_DEPOT (1.3x cost, MEDIUM risk)
    13‚Üí * 5. ADD_CONTRACTOR (2.0x cost, MEDIUM risk)
    14‚Üí * 6. MANUAL_REVIEW (flagged for high unresolvable overload)
    15‚Üí *
    16‚Üí * Job Flow:
